			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" checked="checked" name="bharatratnaawardees" value="Ravi Shankar">Ravi Shankar <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees" value="Bhimsen Joshi">Bhimsen Joshi <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees" value="C. N. R. Rao">C. N. R. Rao <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees" value="Sachin Tendulkar" id="correct_1">Sachin Tendulkar <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>	
			<h2>Q2 Won the award in 2001 and was a renowned Hindustani classical shehnai player ?</h2>
			<aside><p>1 point</p></aside>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" checked="checked" name="bharatratnaawardees_1" value="Lata Mangeshkar">Lata Mangeshkar <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees_1" value="J. R. D. Tata">J. R. D. Tata <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees_1" value="Ustad Bismillah Khan" id="correct_2">Ustad Bismillah Khan <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees_1" value="Morarji Desai">Morarji Desai <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<h2>Q3 Won the award in 2015. Parliamentarian for over four decades and a former prime minister ?</h2>
			<aside><p>1 point</p></aside>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" checked="checked" name="bharatratnaawardees_2" value="Atal Bihari Vajpayee" id="correct_3">Atal Bihari Vajpayee <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees_2" value="Gopinath Bordoloi">Gopinath Bordoloi <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees_2" value="Amartya Sen">Amartya Sen <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<label class="transform"><input type="radio" name="bharatratnaawardees_2" value="Satyajit Ray">Satyajit Ray <span class="correct"></span></label><br/>
			<input type="button" value="Submit" name="submission" class="transform_1" onclick="score()">
		</form>	
	</main>
</body>
</html>